<title>
DTC B1188
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70AA314018001">
<title>
Detektirano DTC stanje i problematično područje
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.229in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.966in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Detektirano DTC stanje
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Problematično područje
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1188: Komunikacijska pogreška primopredajnika
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Pogreška potvrde između ključa za pokretanje i BCM-a.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Ključ za pokretanje nije registriran
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Ključ za pokretanje 
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
BCM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70AA314018002">
<title>
Rješavanje problema DTC-a
</title>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Prije rješavanja problema obavezno pročitajte upute u 
<intxref refid = "AHRAP70AA310002">Mjere opreza za sustav blokade motora:Model s kontakt bravom</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Ako se radi o BCM-u koji je bio registriran u drugom vozilu (prethodno korištena stavka), ključ za pokretanje ne može se registrirati. Kada je zamjena neophodna, uvijek ugradite novi BCM.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<diag type = "test" id = "AHRAP70AA314018003">
<testgroup id = "AHRAP70AA314018004">
<title>
Provjera pokretanja motora
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Pokrenite motor pomoću rezervnog ključa za pokretanje.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Je li se motor pokrenuo?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Kraj. (Ključ za pokretanje nije registriran)
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Idite na 2. korak.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AHRAP70AA314018005">
<title>
Registracija ključa za pokretanje
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Izvršite &#34;Registraciju ključa blokade motora&#34;. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70AA316002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Uvjerite se da je kontakt isključen.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Uključite kontakt.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Ponovno provjerite DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70AA314003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Detektira li se i dalje DTC B1188?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Zamijenite BCM i ponovo provjerite DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70AA206003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Kraj. (Ključ za pokretanje nije registriran)
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
